I don't think this is quite right.  Today it is valid to pass the action as a register option as long as it is set to 'register'.  So this could possibly break existing code.
What do you think of this instead?
type KeycloakRegisterOptions = Omit<KeycloakLoginOptions, 'action'> & {action?: 'register'}

